description:
Kenny Baron's Masterclass during Leopolis Jazz Fest 2019. Lviv, Ukraine.
Jazz legend talk about his favorite pianists that inspired him and play in style of Tommy Flanagan, Thelonius Monk, Art Tatum, Bud Powell.
title: Kenny Baron Masterclass - Influences (ENG/UKR)
